{
  "design_notes": "The chart is designed as a Hard difficulty progression aligning with the high-energy electro-pop structure. The intro scales from simple quarter-beat footsteps to slightly denser eighth steps. The first drop introduces physical movement across the pad with flowing zigzag streams and short hold locks. The build-up is mapped sparsely with steps to offer breathing room before Drop 2. Drop 2 ramps up the physical exertion using jumps and crossover-rich 16th stream steps. After a brief bar transition, the climax drop drives the movement hardest with dense streams, before tapering down gracefully into the outro decay.",
